{
  "texts": [
    "Various faculties and university regions are well represented, underlining the study's inclusivity and the potential applicability of the findings across different academic domains and geographic regions.",
    "This diverse demographic composition ensures that the study's outcomes consider a range of perspectives and experiences, thus enhancing the richness and relevance of the research findings as noted by (Hennink et al., 2020).",
    "Furthermore, the interview questions encompassed a combination of closed and open-ended questions.",
    "These questions were designed to delve into the participants' experiences with ChatGPT, probing for insights into any encountered challenges, strategies for integrating the model into their work, and recommendations for potential enhancements.",
    "Following the completion and recording of the interviews, transcription was carried out using two distinct tools, namely Otter4 and Temi5."
  ]
}